Package io.github.tomaso2468.rpgonline.net.login

A package for handling login servers.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    ServerProtocol
    An interface representing a web connection.
    UserServer
    An interface providing methods for accessing login servers.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    HTTPProtocol
    A web connection using the HTTP-POST method.
    HTTPSProtocol
    A web connection using the HTTPS-POST method.
    LocalDiskUserServer
    A user server stored in appdata on the local disk.
    LocalDiskUserServer.Database
    A class storing local user data.
    LocalDiskUserServer.User
    A representation of a user.
    MultiUserServer
    A user server that combines multiple servers in a priority list.
    MultiUserServer.DownServer
    A server used if not other server can be found.
    WebUserServer
    A user server that automatically picks the best protocol for a URL.
